title: TAVIK | Featured Video: Nothing Tee
description:
The NOTHING t-shirt takes you to a relaxed state of mind. 
This vintage washed tee gets better with age so make sure you wear the shit out of it! With a cool print logo on the back, "Nothing on my mind" is exactly how you'll feel while wearing this tee.
